竟然徒手㩒死隻甲由就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢講話取消翻個飯因爲唔知隻甲由有冇爬過入去兜飯度<br />\n死肥仔侍應：哦，唔要咪唔要囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲態度閪到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地下又痴笠笠 <br />\n仲要一坐低個侍應9 dum本menu喺枱面倒瀉哂兜醬都唔攞返啲紙巾嚟抹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n價錢又唔係平 但又當你狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後都唔會再幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8269e56b2db9dc3ce3929465c9ede021dbaaccf","tid":1096813,"uid":43095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b22862c53d7e0706457e6afe729bd49d053999b","tid":1096813,"uid":37746,"like":245,"dislike":8,"score":237,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"上次食到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />blacklisted"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"有次生日食完病撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac5f173654464af66399ce6e0d44a927f575476","tid":1096813,"uid":55445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T14:20:29.000Z","msg":"真正既窮人我食唐記外賣飯盒炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1271f8dd1d2922a3034fa453c5845c639f8571a","tid":1096813,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T14:56:39.000Z","msg":"其實間野都真係好污糟下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n碗碟枱都勁油"},{"pid":"7ddf247e71501192f0f3ebc6fc508ce7ff9b4d5e","tid":1096813,"uid":153570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:10:52.000Z","msg":"食唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f37009da55b4b8e668f514b74be83368a8b7a5","tid":1096813,"uid":124331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"沙田個間次次食都肚痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f0cbe7c66bc9c3e3bca3ddfcb0bf827459ed2d","tid":1096813,"uid":11088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38f2ae3d4717a86ba78d721c75b21b87ed58ca15","tid":1096813,"uid":34177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64ce49af6cc25f7520b27e32b1a1ce2f17ab5cdb","tid":1096813,"uid":237227,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"我本身勁憎食泡菜，但佢嗰度啲泡菜我居然會食曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知邊度買，斷估唔係自己醃掛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:15:34.000Z","msg":"佢依家有得賣 68蚊一盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢d菜類好乾淨好厚身<br />\n泡菜仲好食過韓國食個d<br />\n有無炑八職員話我知係邊到既生菜<br />\n好奇左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:17:16.000Z","msg":"其實都係黃芽白，但佢個係自己醃和醃製上個味甜啲，個口味比較啱香港人<br />\n利申：前員工"},{"pid":"f4d223a16eae9390cf91b3939262ad0acc555cf1","tid":1096813,"uid":70042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:28:04.000Z","msg":"個fd食完發燒<br />\n但我又無咩事喎"},{"pid":"efe072f0b2d1468285753e815737308448f2c032","tid":1096813,"uid":86199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:29:24.000Z","msg":"上次食完又痾又嘔，唔會再去"},{"pid":"e36961fcfbda554527e822310bae11745969e80a","tid":1096813,"uid":77731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T16:12:15.000Z","msg":"成700個打手"},{"pid":"a5e9f858ad1436db08f90b93695d92fc36339093","tid":1096813,"uid":237227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38f2ae3d4717a86ba78d721c75b21b87ed58ca15","tid":1096813,"uid":34177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64ce49af6cc25f7520b27e32b1a1ce2f17ab5cdb","tid":1096813,"uid":237227,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"我本身勁憎食泡菜，但佢嗰度啲泡菜我居然會食曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知邊度買，斷估唔係自己醃掛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2